OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the afternoon. Becoming
OL,7,Fcloudy overnight with low cloud and
OL,8,Ffog coming off the North Sea and
OL,9,Fspreading slowly westwards by the
OL,10,Fmorning. Temperatures remaining mild
OL,11,Ftonight but cooler along the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FLow cloud and fog lingering
OL,14,Ffor most. A moderate easterly wind
OL,15,Fwill keep temperatures a lot cooler
OL,16,Fthan of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
