OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fperiods throughout Sunday, though
OL,7,Fbrighter in the afternoon. Dry and
OL,8,Flargely sunny conditions on Monday
OL,9,Fwith coastal cloud. Some patchy cloud
OL,10,FTuesday morning, brightening up later.
OL,11,FTemperatures around average.
